# v4 Phase 0: canonical decision records (ADRs) are committed even though
# docs/ is otherwise ignored. Pattern: ignore docs/ contents but not the
# directory itself, then re-include docs/decisions/. (`docs/` alone would
# exclude the directory so the `!docs/decisions/` exception couldn't work.)
docs/*
!docs/decisions/
!docs/decisions/**
